  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> July 18, 2025</p>

  <p>This extension, <strong>Subliminal Affirmations Flasher</strong>, respects your privacy and complies with the policies of the Chrome Web Store.</p>

  <h2>1. Data Collection</h2>
  <p>We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal or sensitive user data. All affirmations and settings are stored locally on your device.</p>

  <h2>2. Local Storage</h2>
  <p>Settings and user-added affirmations are saved using Chromeâ€™s <code>storage</code> API to provide a consistent experience across sessions. No data leaves your device.</p>

  <h2>3. No Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>This extension does not use third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.</p>

  <h2>4. Permissions</h2>
  <p>The extension requires limited permissions (like scripting and storage) to inject and flash affirmations on active pages. These are used only for the core functionality and nothing else.</p>

  <h2>5. Security</h2>
  <p>All code runs locally. No external scripts or remote code execution is involved, ensuring full user control and safety.</p>

  <h2>6. Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this policy, contact us at: <a href="mailto:your.email@example.com">your.email@example.com</a></p>

